lambdamagic.data

インタフェース Queryable<T1,T2>

  • 型パラメータ:
    T1 - query type
    T2 - output type of query
    既知のサブインタフェースのリスト:
    PropertySet<T>
    既知の実装クラスのリスト:
    HttpCookie, InMemoryPropertySet, PropertyString, Settings

    public interface Queryable<T1,T2>
    An interface that indicates given object receive the query of type T1 and return the value of type T2 depending on the query. Typically, type T1 is String.
    作成者:
    koiketakayuki

    • メソッドのサマリー

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods 
      修飾子とタイプ メソッドと説明
      T2 get(T1 propertyName)
      Receive the query of type T1 and return the value of type T2.

    • メソッドの詳細

      • get

        T2 get(T1 propertyName)
        Receive the query of type T1 and return the value of type T2.
        パラメータ:
        propertyName - query of type T1 that specifies the property name
        戻り値:
        output of type T2
